author: alexdma
msg: Introduces a POST service for refactoring (refactor/applyfile) that extracts the recipe from a plain text file. This is useful if e.g. the recipe is too long to be supplied as a string to a curl command, as per STANBOL-143 and STANBOL-181. For convenience, a RuleParserImpl.parse(InputStream) method is introduced.
